                Blood is the most precious gift that that anyone can give to<br>
                another person - the gift of life . A decision to donate your<br> 
                blood can save a life ,or even several if your blood is separated<br>
                into its components -red cells,platelets and plasma -which can be used<br>
                individually for patients with specific conditions.</ul>
